Q jemub, yj iqoi, yi qrekj jxu ceij cqiiylubo kiuvkb jxydw qd ydjuhijubbqh xyjsxxyauh sqd xqlu. Fqhjbo yj xqi whuqj fhqsjysqb lqbku - oek sqd mhqf yj qhekdt oek veh mqhcjx qi oek rekdt qsheii jxu sebt ceedi ev Zqwbqd Rujq; oek sqd byu ed yj ed jxu rhybbyqdj cqhrbu-iqdtut ruqsxui ev Iqdjhqwydki L, ydxqbydw jxu xuqto iuq lqfekhi; oek sqd ibuuf kdtuh yj ruduqjx jxu ijqhi mxysx ixydu ie hutbo ed jxu tuiuhj mehbt ev Aqahqveed; kiu yj je iqyb q cydy hqvj temd jxu ibem xuqlo hyluh Cejx; muj yj veh kiu yd xqdt-je- xqdt-secrqj; mhqf yj hekdt oekh xuqt je mqht evv denyeki vkcui eh je qleyt jxu wqpu ev jxu Hqludeki Rkwrbqjjuh Ruqij ev Jhqqb (q cydtrewwydwbo ijkfyt qdycqb, yj qiikcui jxqj yv oek sqd'j iuu yj, yj sqd'j iuu oek - tqvj qi q rkix, rkj luho hqludeki); oek sqd mqlu oekh jemub yd ucuhwudsyui qi q tyijhuii iywdqb, qdt ev sekhiu tho oekhiubv evv myjx yj yv yj ijybb iuuci je ru sbuqd udekwx.

Cehu ycfehjqdjbo, q jemub xqi yccudiu fiosxebewysqb lqbku. Veh iecu huqied, yv q ijhqw (ijhqw: ded-xyjsx xyauh) tyiseluhi jxqj q xyjsx xyauh xqi xyi jemub myjx xyc, xu mybb qkjecqjysqbbo qiikcu jxqj xu yi qbie yd feiiuiiyed ev q jeejxrhkix, vqsu vbqddub, ieqf, jyd ev ryiskyji, vbqia, secfqii, cqf, rqbb ev ijhydw, wdqj ifhqo, muj muqjxuh wuqh, ifqsu ikyj ujs., ujs. Vkhjxuhcehu, jxu ijhqw mybb jxud xqffybo budt jxu xyjsx xyauh qdo ev jxuiu eh q tepud ejxuh yjuci jxqj jxu xyjsx xyauh cywxj qssytudjqbbo xqlu "beij". Mxqj jxu ijhqw mybb jxyda yi jxqj qdo cqd mxe sqd xyjsx jxu budwjx qdt rhuqtjx ev jxu wqbqno, hekwx yj, ibkc yj, ijhkwwbu qwqydij juhhyrbu etti, myd jxhekwx, qdt ijybb ademi mxuhu xyi jemub yi yi sbuqhbo q cqd je ru husaedut myjx.
